{
  "texts": [
    "As for MM-SADA, the original approach works only with RGB and Flow modalities.",
    "Therefore, to integrate the Audio modality, we use two separate branches, one for RGB-Flow and the other for RGB-Audio modalities (as in Planamente et al. (2022)).",
    "The adversarial branch is applied individually to each modality.",
    "Results are given as Top-1 and Top-5 accuracy for verb, noun, and action (Table 5).",
    "For each baseline, we also report the relative \"Source Only\", average improvement in terms of Top-1 accuracy."
  ]
}